'''安德魯·哈斯提'''（Andrew Hastie，{{bd|1982年|9月30日}}）是一位[[澳洲|澳洲]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[澳洲自由黨|澳洲自由黨]]。现任澳大利亚{{le|国会情报和安全联合委员会|Parliamentary Joint Committee on Intelligence and Security}}主席。自2015年開始，他是[[坎寧_(澳大利亞國會選區)|坎寧]]選區選出的[[澳大利亚众议院|澳大利亚众议院]]的議員。他曾擔任空军特别部队上尉<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-09-19/andrew-hastie-wins-canning-by-election/6789334 | publisher=ABC News | title=Canning by-election: Liberal candidate Andrew Hastie wins by-election | date=19 September 2015 | accessdate=20 September 2015 | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108185757/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-09-19/andrew-hastie-wins-canning-by-election/6789334 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/wa/a/29575981/live-blog-andrew-hastie-claims-canning-in-byelection/ | publisher=The West Australian | title=Andrew Hastie claims Canning in by election | date=19 September 2015 | accessdate=20 September 2015 | archive-date=2016-03-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322154846/https://au.news.yahoo.com/thewest/wa/a/29575981/live-blog-andrew-hastie-claims-canning-in-byelection/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.smh.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/canning-byelection-liberal-candidate-andrew-hastie-set-for-win-over-matt-keogh-20150919-gjqjv1.html/ | publisher=Sydney Morning Herald | title=Canning byelection: Liberal candidate Andrew Hastie wins as Matt Keogh concedes | date=20 September 2015 | accessdate=20 September 2015 | archive-date=2016-12-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222083709/http://www.smh.com.au/federal-politics/political-news/canning-byelection-liberal-candidate-andrew-hastie-set-for-win-over-matt-keogh-20150919-gjqjv1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年8月7日，哈斯提在《[[悉尼先驱晨报|悉尼先驱晨报]]》上发表文章，认为西方误判了中国，错认为中国的经济自由会导致民主，他拿中国与第二次世界大战时的[[納粹德国|納粹德国]]比较。<ref>{{cite news |title=澳一众议员警告中国威胁或如当年纳粹德国 中国强烈不满 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Denounces-Australian-Lawmaker-Remark-On-Nazi-Germany-20190808/5033971.html |accessdate=2019-08-08 |agency=美国之音 |date=2019年8月8日 |archive-date=2019-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217165959/https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Denounces-Australian-Lawmaker-Remark-On-Nazi-Germany-20190808/5033971.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年12月18日獲任命為助理国防部长<ref>{{cite news |title=澳大利亚调整内阁 对华鹰派力量抬头？ |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%86%85%E9%98%81-%E5%AF%B9%E5%8D%8E%E9%B9%B0%E6%B4%BE%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E6%8A%AC%E5%A4%B4/a-55983840 |accessdate=2020-12-19 |archive-date=2021-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210529081921/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%86%85%E9%98%81-%E5%AF%B9%E5%8D%8E%E9%B9%B0%E6%B4%BE%E5%8A%9B%E9%87%8F%E6%8A%AC%E5%A4%B4/a-55983840 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

